### Get all orders (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/orders
Accept: application/json

### Get all orders with page size
GET http://localhost:8082/api/orders?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Get orders by customer email
GET http://localhost:8082/api/orders/customer/john.doe@example.com
Accept: application/json

### Get orders by status (PENDING)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/orders/status/PENDING
Accept: application/json

### Create a new order
POST http://localhost:8082/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Michael Scott",
  "customerEmail": "michael.scott@dundermifflin.com",
  "shippingAddress": "1725 Slough Avenue, Scranton, PA 18540",
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "productId": 4,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Create another order with multiple quantities
POST http://localhost:8082/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Dwight Schrute",
  "customerEmail": "dwight.schrute@dundermifflin.com",
  "shippingAddress": "Schrute Farms, Honesdale, PA 18431",
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": 7,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 10,
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

### Update order status to CONFIRMED
PATCH http://localhost:8082/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

### Delete order
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/orders/3
Accept: application/json

